reviewText:
I LOVE THIS HOODIE. Super comfortable, love deftones, has a unique design on it, nice hoodie to layer with.
HOWEVER;
Shrinks in wash/dryer. Definitely want to hang dry this hoodie. I've had it for a little while now but it's already made it into the dryer accidentally and boy did it shrink noticeably. Probably should mention that it comes in the mail somewhere between a medium and a large, of course I'm also stupid tall so it might fit someone who's under 6' better. Either way, hang dry it and it shouldn't shrink too much. Just don't spill/drip/drop any food/drink on it and you should be fine. For $13 it's worth it.

The dress is beautiful, but the fabric is so cheap

